728356f-a.folder: Arthur Kill Road & Clarke Avenue, Staten Island, NY
728356f-a.original_title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Clarke Avenue
728356f-a.text:
135 Arthur Kill Road, north side, west of Clarke Avenue, showing the auto wrecking place of the Richmond Auto Wrecking Company. It is situated on the
former C.M. Connor (Conner) property.
May 9, 1935
Views 1, 2
P. L. Sperr
